    feat: Implement complete job application system for freelancers
    
     Features Added:
    - Dual-mode job board (template jobs for public, real jobs for logged-in users)
    - Dynamic button states (Apply Now/Runner Up/Job Filled) based on slot availability
    - Job application system with slot management (primary/runner-up)
    - Email notifications to admin when applications are submitted
    - Auto-removal of expired jobs (moves past-due jobs to inactive status)
    - Admin panel for job management at /admin/jobs
    - Authentication integration with Supabase
    
     Technical Implementation:
    - Created enhanced job board component with authentication awareness
    - Built comprehensive API routes for jobs, applications, and admin functions
    - Added useAuth hook for authentication state management
    - Implemented database schema updates for slots and application tracking
    - Added email notification system with Resend API integration
    
     Files Added/Modified:
    - components/job-board-enhanced.tsx - Main job board with dual functionality
    - hooks/use-auth.ts - Authentication state management
    - app/api/jobs/* - Job management API endpoints
    - app/api/admin/jobs/* - Admin API endpoints
    - app/admin/jobs/page.tsx - Admin job management interface
    - Updated README.md with new database schema
    - Created SETUP.md with comprehensive setup guide
    
     User Experience:
    - Public users see template jobs with redirects to application form
    - Logged-in freelancers see real jobs with dynamic application buttons
    - Admin can manage jobs and view applications
    - Automatic cleanup of expired opportunities
    - Real-time slot availability tracking

